- Mirrored the same logic in triple-generation path in [codec.py](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-vector-8h-20260518T072401Z-codex-ir_decompiler/worktrees/agent-codex-ir_decompiler-packet-000042-20260518_112935/ipfs_datasets_py/logic/modal/codec.py:171) and [codec.py](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-vector-8h-20260518T072401Z-codex-ir_decompiler/worktrees/agent-codex-ir_decompiler-packet-000042-20260518_112935/ipfs_datasets_py/logic/modal/codec.py:2041).
